preference.name: TC_Enable_Quantity_UoMs
preference.preference_description: (Deprecated) This is deprecated in Teamcenter 13.1.0.4 and will be removed after Teamcenter 14. Defines the behavior to create "Quantity Managed" occurrences. For a given part structure, if a valid quantity value and a Unit of Measure (UoM) is defined, additional occurrences will be created. Valid values are the symbols for Units of Measure.
